{"tid":1740121,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁咏欣 啟德中及南 啟德400米外地盤疑有致癌物堆積","createTime":"2019-11-20T00:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T02:48:09.000Z","uid":106800,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f129aebddaf401d271c2cd814896e687e512837","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:08:03.000Z","msg":"#啟德400米外地盤疑有致癌物堆積<br />\n#如屬實恐會吹向啟德影響居民健康<br />\n<br />\n我收到居民反映，指近日有大量懷疑含有有害物質二噁英的雜物，棄置在距離啟德約400米的宏照道路政署地盤內。<br />\n<br />\n兩個月前，我曾向路政署查詢廢棄物的來源，路政回覆，原來有關棄置物是在公眾運動後，警方在現場收集的物證。<br />\n<br />\n昨天（11月16日），麗晶花園居民發現大量雜物在晚間運到上址，極可能是公眾運動後清理的路障，懷疑含有極度致癌物二噁英於其中。<br />\n<br />\n注：(來源：網上資料)<br />\n#甚麼是二噁英<br />\n-二噁英是一類常見的持久性環境污染物。<br />\n<br />\n#二噁英的特性<br />\n-極其穩定，能在環境中長存數十年，不受破壞<br />\n-毒性極高，會導致生育和發育問題、破壞免疫系統、干擾荷爾蒙分泌以及致癌<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動由6月至今，警方在驅散行動中共發射超過9,300枚催淚彈，催淚彈主要成分CS釋放出毒性極強的類二噁英，危害公眾健康。<br />\n<br />\n#會影響啟德居民嗎<br />\n地盤位於啟德以東方向的400米左右，未知會否被風向吹到啟德。<br />\n<br />\n#跟進<br />\n本人要求提供環境調查報告及實地分析數據，確保附近環境不被有害物質污染。<br />\n<br />\n(圖片來源：麗晶花園居民)<br />\n<br />\n#啟德 #啟德一號 #德朗邨 #朗朗苑 #天寰 #嘉匯 #龍譽 #oasis<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=538730413522758&amp;id=414955815900219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D538730413522758%26id%3D414955815900219&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=cd195ca1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=538730413522758&amp;id=414955815900219</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=540741493321650&amp;id=414955815900219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D540741493321650%26id%3D414955815900219&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=0b5f92b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=540741493321650&amp;id=414955815900219</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢區好危<br />\n但都要幫下手<br />\n有冇人幫手整文宣 最好係banner<br />\n港豬同nd人 净係識睇banner<br />\n選舉戰線要人"},{"pid":"20ca106c4ca35fe499a1aced64796a1bd975f41f","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:09:59.000Z","msg":"一嚟就負皮"},{"pid":"bfe71f72e740f3b122b266172720cbd332367171","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:10:13.000Z","msg":"言都唔留jm9"},{"pid":"b27df377baba9296d775911f84a5951e53d4dd11","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:10:56.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"48c69010fc825c85fb8fb214444e71f3fb41bbe3","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:11:10.000Z","msg":"幫手"},{"pid":"8cfbb7b40b5d976fc37982bbdf0f5900b78c9c29","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"做咗野都冇人知"},{"pid":"c8b1b939d3c0749a25caff4ec6ae7bb5c3764d86","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:11:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0e27fe4c214a4e9acc7973dae20cb413591724d","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:11:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a8126fb694a70dbc71da734a6f06ade1bec8681","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:11:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cbf16ce3260c13682a0855f9a0dcf6482ab620e","tid":1740121,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:12:02.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"95dbfc969451f1ea0b641217715f748aac476784","tid":1740121,"uid":18546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:12:06.000Z","msg":"飲鉛水投DAB 吸下毒氣有咩問題"},{"pid":"f6602db490b5e49fffadc262b20f24dbbe6ca277","tid":1740121,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:13:48.000Z","msg":"唔怪得晚晚咁撚嘈<br />\n死仆街港共"},{"pid":"c0e3d403d36324efcd7c764127625